Package: opdesmixr
Type: Package
Title: Optimal experimental designs for mixture models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Mario H. Becerra
Maintainer: Mario H. Becerra <becerra.mario.h@gmail.com>
Description: An implementatio of algorithms to find optimal experimental designs for mixtures using
    ScheffÃ© models. A mixture experiment is one in which there is an equality constraint.
    This is usually that the ingredients must sum up to 1 because they represent proportions of 
    ingredients. It supports Gaussian and Multinomial Logit (MNL) models.
